				\begin{document}$$\hbox {MoS}_2$$\end{document} layer is created at lower thermal exposure, again suggesting a more complete sulfurization. MoS2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
