Overview of effects of different thermal exposure during pre-annealing. Figure inspired by5.

In the as-deposited films, a Cu–Sn–S phase was detected in all samples, and SnS flakes and traces of a Cu–S phase in the films prepared at 250∘C\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
