Films were deposited through spin-coating (on a KW-4A spin-coater from MicroNanoTools) with a chuck suitable for the size of the sample. The substrates used were Mo-coated soda lime glass (SLG) of 1 mm thickness (from ZSW), and they were cleaned in a 1:1 Milli-Q water (from Millipore Corp, 18.2MΩcm\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
