The as-deposited samples were sulfurized in a closed graphite box (from Mersen Nordic) containing 100 mg S powder (99.998%) in a tube furnace (from Hobersal). The chamber was evacuated to a base pressure of <10-2\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
